16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_667656424\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- Vinerea Mare, ultima zi de vineri înaintea Pa&#351;telui;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_533181459\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1250\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_533181459\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- prima &#351;i a doua zi de Pa&#351;ti;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1922148107\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1249\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1922148107\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- 1 mai;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_33220395\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1248\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_33220395\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- 1 iunie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_49855480\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1247\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_49855480\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- prima &#351;i a doua zi de Rusalii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1431836143\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1246\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1431836143\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- Adormirea Maicii Domnului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1619342851\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1245\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1619342851\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- 30 noiembrie - Sfântul Apostol Andrei, cel Întâi chemat,\nOcrotitorul României;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_471735767\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1244\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_471735767\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- 1 decembrie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_406807308\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1243\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_406807308\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- prima &#351;i a doua zi de Cr&#259;ciun;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_842928933\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1242\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_842928933\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- dou&#259; zile pentru fiecare dintre cele 3\ns&#259;rb&#259;tori religioase anuale, declarate astfel de cultele religioase\nlegale, altele decât cele cre&#351;tine, pentru persoanele apar&#355;inând\nacestora.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Acordarea zilelor libere se face\nde c&#259;tre angajator.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_117828215\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1241\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_117828215\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2<sup>1</sup>)Pentru salaria&#355;ii care apar&#355;in de\nun cult religios legal, cre&#351;tin, zilele libere pentru Vinerea Mare -\nultima zi de vineri înaintea Pa&#351;telui, prima &#351;i a doua zi de\nPa&#351;ti, prima &#351;i a doua zi de Rusalii se acord&#259; în func&#355;ie\nde data la care sunt celebrate de acel cult.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_467044107\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1240\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_467044107\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Zilele libere stabilite potrivit alin. (1) pentru\npersoanele apar&#355;inând cultelor religioase legale, altele decât cele\ncre&#351;tine, se acord&#259; de c&#259;tre angajator în alte zile decât zilele\nde s&#259;rb&#259;toare legal&#259; stabilite potrivit legii sau de concediu de\nodihn&#259; anual.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_55301466\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1239\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_55301466\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3<sup>1</sup>)Salaria&#355;ii care au beneficiat de zilele\nlibere pentru Vinerea Mare - ultima zi de vineri înaintea Pa&#351;telui, prima\n&#351;i a doua zi de Pa&#351;ti, prima &#351;i a doua zi de Rusalii, atât la\ndatele stabilite pentru cultul religios legal, cre&#351;tin, de care\napar&#355;in, cât &#351;i pentru alt cult cre&#351;tin, vor recupera zilele\nlibere suplimentare pe baza unui program stabilit de angajator.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1206967113\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1238\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1206967113\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Pân&#259; la data de 15 ianuarie a fiec&#259;rui an, se\nstabilesc prin hot&#259;râre a Guvernului, pentru personalul din sistemul\nbugetar, zilele lucr&#259;toare pentru care se acord&#259; zile libere, zile\ncare preced&#259; &#351;i/sau care succed&#259; zilelor de s&#259;rb&#259;toare\nlegal&#259; în care nu se lucreaz&#259;, prev&#259;zute la alin. (1), precum\n&#351;i zilele în care se recupereaz&#259; orele de munc&#259; neefectuate.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}